  "technicalDetails": "<p>Basic Features</p><ol><li>Physical assembly system</li><li>Disassembly function</li><li>Object grabbing capability</li><li>Assembly save function</li><li>Sandbox vehicle control system</li><li>Fully decoupled, allowing you to customize your assembly methods</li><li>Customizable, enabling you to modify the physics actors based on video tutorials</li></ol><p>Dependency&#xff1a;Water Plugins</p><p>C&#43;&#43; : No ,Pure Blueprints</p><p>Number of Blueprints: 45</p><p>Number of Mesh: 13</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms:</p><p>Windows: (Yes)</p>",
